{"name":"Geralt of Rivia","nameCn":"杰洛特","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/e9/83/25981_crt_5MX7z.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>杰洛特</li><li><span>别名: </span>利维亚的杰洛特</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Geralt of Rivia</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>リヴィアのゲラルト</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>白狼 老滚</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Geralt z Rivii</li><li><span>性别: </span>男</li>","detail":"A Witcher! Hide your women!<br />杰洛特（Geralt of Rivia）是由波兰作家Andrzej Sapkowski创造的一个奇幻人物，在其系列小说和游戏《巫师》（The Witcher）系列中担任主角，主人公Geralt是一名年轻的经验丰富的狩魔猎人，<br />他健谈、机智且愤世嫉俗，他常常评论自己的冒险和经历。他的事迹大多由最佳损友丹德利恩记录并传唱。虽然外表看上去是人类，但是他已经是变异的种族了：又高又瘦，非自然的白发（因此得名白狼）、眼睛和肤色，虽然不是很美观，但是有一种特别的帅气，他的触碰对女性是强烈刺激，但没有生育能力，这是他从小就服下特殊药剂诱发变异的后果。狩魔猎人在这个时代已经变得非常稀少。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/218023","name":"Wiedźmin","nameCn":"猎魔人","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/6d/e2/218023_s7mmH.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/18174","name":"The Witcher 2: Assassins of Kings","nameCn":"巫师2：国王刺客","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/0f/00/18174_zzp6G.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/18173","name":"The Witcher","nameCn":"巫师","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/9e/bd/18173_JbJFx.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/262220","name":"The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt – Blood and Wine","nameCn":"巫师3：狂猎－血与酒","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/07/a5/262220_hIyGG.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/66198","name":"The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt","nameCn":"巫师3：狂猎","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/d4/31/66198_vgcwp.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"山路和弘","castHref":"/person/5503","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/9c/ff/5503_prsn_5daNH.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/262219","name":"The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt - Hearts of Stone","nameCn":"巫师3：狂猎－石之心","cover":"//lain.